WEBVTT

00:07:59.560 --> 00:08:00.776
And he said, "Yep."

00:08:00.800 --> 00:08:03.576
And he said, "Wow.
How many games are you going to miss?"

00:08:03.600 --> 00:08:05.376
(Laughter)

00:08:05.400 --> 00:08:06.616
True story.

00:08:06.640 --> 00:08:09.200
(Laughter)

00:08:12.800 --> 00:08:16.016
But we've been remarkably successful --

00:08:16.040 --> 00:08:19.496
over 2,500 athletes have signed up.

00:08:19.520 --> 00:08:22.856
They get a brain-donation card
they keep in their wallet.

00:08:22.880 --> 00:08:26.600
This is mine, I was
obviously first, it says 01.

00:08:27.360 --> 00:08:29.096
And I will donate my brain to this.

00:08:29.120 --> 00:08:31.856
We've also been lucky
to have people like Brandi Chastain,